title: Front Range Christian downs Bobcats 20-14 Friday night
text: Front Range Christian downs Bobcats 20-14 Friday night Trail-Gazette staff Posted: 10/10/2015 11:55:11 AM MDT The Front Range Christian Falcons spoiled the Estes Park High School Bobcats' homecoming game Friday night, leaving town with a 20-14 victory. Scoring touchdowns for the Bobcats were senior running back Sam Addison and senior quarterback Joseph Coleson. Addison also scored on a 2-point conversion try. (Photos by Debbie Holmes / Estes Park Trail-Gazette) 8px;">Read more in Wednesday's Trail-Gazette. Advertisement
